OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784726326
OL,3,CFirefighters tackling 'significant'
OL,4,Cwildfire in Blaenavon
OL,6,FFire crews remain at the scene of a
OL,7,F"significant" wildfire covering nearly
OL,8,F200 acres of land in Blaenavon.
OL,10,FCrews from South Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,11,FService (SWFRS) spent the night
OL,12,Fdealing with the fire, having received
OL,13,Fan initial call on Sunday evening.
OL,15,FSix appliances and a water bowser
OL,16,Fremain at the scene, supported by
OL,17,FSWFRS tactical wildfire officers who
OL,18,Fare specially trained in responding to
OL,19,Fthese incidents.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
