PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784726326
OL,3,CFirefighters tackling 'significant'
OL,4,Cwildfire in Blaenavon
OL,6,FThe wildfire currently covers around
OL,7,F80 hectares of mixed land of bracken
OL,8,Fand gorse - which equates to nearly
OL,9,F200 acres of land.
OL,11,FCrews have been working in challenging
OL,12,Fconditions due to the terrain, access
OL,13,Fand the wind conditions, the service
OL,14,Fsaid.
OL,16,F"A change in wind direction overnight
OL,17,Fhas seen smoke from the incident
OL,18,Fimpacting a large area of South Wales,
OL,19,Fand is reported as far south as
OL,20,FCaerphilly and Cardiff," a
OL,21,Fspokesperson from SWFRS said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,434,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1784726326
OL,3,CFirefighters tackling 'significant'
OL,4,Cwildfire in Blaenavon
OL,6,F"SWFRS is advising anyone affected by
OL,7,Fthis smoke to close their windows and
OL,8,Fdoors.
OL,10,F"SWFRS is receiving a high volume of
OL,11,Fcalls reporting the smoke, however the
OL,12,FService would like to reassure
OL,13,Fcommunities that they are aware and
OL,14,Fare dealing with the incident which
OL,15,Fhas caused it.
OL,17,F"People are being advised to stay away
OL,18,Ffrom the area, to allow the emergency
OL,19,Fresponse to continue."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/3
